title: Phone Calls From The Dead | Horror Podcast
description:
Today on an episode of Real Ghost Stories online that is sure to traumatize your neighbor’s ass-hole dog. 

Real people, in real situations, share their traumatizing ghost stories with us. 

Hoping that you can understand and relate to the shocking and sometimes malevolent supernatural activity they suffer with. 

And maybe, just maybe, you can help to solve a paranormal Unsolved Mystery, Today, On Real Ghost Stories Online.

If you have a real ghost story or supernatural event to report, please write into our show or call 1-855-853-4802!
If you like the show, please help keep us on the air and support the show by becoming an EPP (Extra Podcast Person). We'll give you a BONUS episode every week as a "Thank You" for your support.
